ActStandards Council of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of CHARLES (CHUCK) LAFLECHE of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Irene A. Seiferling, whose term has expired.
